Package net.sf.saxon.sql Description

This package provides some sample extension elements for loading data into an SQL database.

These classes are not intended as a production-quality tool, rather as an illustration of what can be achieved using extension elements.

These SQL extensions are documented in the file sql-extension.html in the main documentation directory.

Michael H. Kay
25 April 2002
